# Weather Dashboard Application

A responsive web app providing real-time weather updates and a 5-day forecast.

## Technologies Used
- Frontend: React.js, CSS3
- API: OpenWeatherMap
- Deployment: GitHub Pages

## Features
- City search
- Weather details
- Temperature unit switch

## Installation
```bash
git clone https://github.com/dzhamal-abdrakhmanov/weather-dashboard.git
cd weather-dashboard
npm install
touch .env # add your OpenWeatherMap API key
npm start
